  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗数据流转的流程图，核心是患者记录如何在HIPAA合规环境下传递。起点是PatientRecords，然后进入HIPAA Vault做加密存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，PatientRecords作为入口节点。HIPAA Vault是加密存储节点对吧？那从Vault出来后数据流向哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Vault解密后数据要同步到EMR系统，这里有个EMR_Sync节点。不过我们的架构里有两个EMR_Sync，一个是主同步，一个是灾备同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以Vault出来先到第一个EMR_Sync，然后再到第二个EMR_Sync做冗余。两个节点我都标记为HealthTech_EMR_Sync可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以，第二个EMR_Sync之后要接入LabAnalyzer进行化验分析。这是关键的数据处理节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加LabAnalyzer节点。现在链条是：PatientRecords → HIPAA Vault → EMR_Sync → EMR_Sync → LabAnalyzer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "LabAnalyzer处理完后，数据需要重新加密回存到HIPAA Vault。这里有个循环回流的逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，LabAnalyzer直接回到同一个HIPAA Vault节点，还是需要区分不同的Vault实例？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "实际上我们有三个HIPAA Vault节点，形成级联加密。LabAnalyzer先到第一个回流Vault，再到第二个，再到第三个，形成三层加密防护。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加三个级联的HIPAA Vault节点。现在从LabAnalyzer出来依次经过Vault1、Vault2、Vault3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第三个Vault之后，数据还要再经过一次LabAnalyzer做最终校验，然后才能闭环回到PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以最终闭环是：第三个Vault → 第二个LabAnalyzer → PatientRecords。这样整个数据生命周期就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，但我再检查一下——两个EMR_Sync节点是顺序执行，三个Vault是级联加密，最后回到PatientRecords完成循环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "抱歉，我刚才漏了一个连接。第三个Vault到第二个LabAnalyzer的箭头还没画，现在补上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，让我再确认下节点数量：起点PatientRecords，然后Vault、两个EMR_Sync、LabAnalyzer、三个Vault、再一个LabAnalyzer，最后回到起点。总共9个节点对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，9个节点：A(PatientRecords)、B(Vault)、C(EMR_Sync)、D(EMR_Sync)、E(LabAnalyzer)、F(Vault)、G(Vault)、H(Vault)、I(LabAnalyzer)，最后I连回A。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "节点命名保持HealthTech前缀很好，这样和RDS里的表名一致。流程图方向用TD从上到下能清晰展示数据流向。",
      "elements_involved": [
