      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已设置为TD垂直布局。所有节点和连线都完成了：A→B→C→D→E→F→G→H→I→A的闭环结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
